  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the present study is to evaluate whether the use of indocyanine green fluorescent
      cholangiography is responsible in a decrease of biliary fistula's rate in patients with liver
      diseases requiring liver resection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
