  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  benin or malignant liver disease with resection of 2 or more segments

          -  liver resection by laparotomy

          -  written consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  previous hepatectomy

          -  emergency surgery

          -  allergy to indocyanine green

          -  allergy to methylene blue

          -  pregnancy or breastfeeding
      </textblock>
